#summary Other printer parts, that can be reprogrammed

= Introduction =

Pointers to specific pages for other parts of the printers that can be reprogrammed:

  * [XeroxPhaser850 Xerox Phaser 850 Maintenance EEPROM]
  * [XeroxPhaser6130ImagingUnit Xerox Phaser 6130/6140 Imaging Unit]
  * [XeroxDocuPrintC1110ImagingUnit Fuji Xerox DocuPrint C1110 Imaging Unit]
  * [XeroxDocuPrintC1618ImagingUnit Fuji Xerox DocuPrint C1618 Imaging Unit]
